  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Toast the tortillas on the cedar planks for 2 minutes on each side",
    "In a bowl, mix together the sliced pickles, sauerkraut, caraway seeds, paprika, salt, and pepper",
    "Spoon the pickle mixture onto the toasted tortillas",
    "Return the tortillas to the oven and bake for an additional 5 minutes",
    "Remove the tortillas from the oven and let cool for 1 minute",
    "Serve the tacos hot on the cedar planks"
